    End If
    Return node
End Process

Process called "build_aggregation_expression" takes aggregation_type as Integer, expr as Integer, line as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Build an aggregation expression (Sum/Average/Count/Minimum/Maximum) over
    Note: a collection. aggregation_type carried in value; collection is the child.
    Let safe_line be line
