End Process

Process called "build_is_within_expression" takes value as Integer, lower_bound as Integer, upper_bound as Integer, is_negated as Integer, line as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Build a bounds-membership expression: value is (not) within lower to upper.
    Note: is_negated stored in value; children order: [value, lower, upper].
    Let safe_line be line
