Process called "build_unless_statement" takes condition as Integer, body as Integer, otherwise_clause as Integer, line as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Build an Unless statement (executes body when condition is false).
    Note: Children order: [condition, body, otherwise_clause].
    If condition is equal to 0:
