    If body is not equal to 0:
        proc ast_node_add_child from AST with node, body
    End If
    If otherwise_clause is not equal to 0:
        proc ast_node_add_child from AST with node, otherwise_clause
    End If
    Return node
End Process

Process called "build_do_while_statement" takes body as Integer, condition as Integer, line as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Build a do-while loop node (body executes at least once, then repeats
